Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time to start school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:12.15,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The first day is so exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:15.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:18.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You seem more nervous \Nthan excited, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:23.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wonder if I'll make friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:27.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and if I'll be able to get along \Nwith my classmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:30.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it all makes me so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.80,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. That is nerve-wracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:37.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be standing on the stage \Nwith the theater troupe soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Think of this as another type of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:46.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, if I can get over freezing up \Nwhenever I'm in front of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:47.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:53.18,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just look! You're talking to us \Nright now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:59.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel like I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Sa... Saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:13.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakuragi... H-H-Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm from the... c-country...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.94,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:53.02,sign_4029_23_Mistaken_Friend,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Mistaken Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.48,sign_4149_24_Fujimiya__Girls_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimiya\N Girls'\NHigh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that was a very unique \Nself-introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Unique?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.62,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.44,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can call you that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.12,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So you lived in the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The... c-country...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:17.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I lived in the mountains \Nand worked as a scarecrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.68,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ventriloquism?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.39,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's a funny way to communicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,They laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.81,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you do as a scarecrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.77,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I'm curious, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.53,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.91,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.91,sign_5374_44_Theater_Society_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Theater Society
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.91,sign_5374_45_Recruiting_Membe,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Recruiting Members
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.26,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:52.80,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, all the fans of Chiaki-chan, \Nthe theater club ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.02,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,put this together over spring break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.41,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You know, since the club went on hiatus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.58,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't get to see you on stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.54,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That makes your fans really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:09.85,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And you seemed really disappointed \Nwhen it went on hiatus, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:14.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So we thought, if we started \Na theater society, you could act again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.61,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Chiaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That ventriloquism talk \Nwent over better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:27.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wasn't able to say a word, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.24,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan! Kuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.74,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's something I wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.75,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Theater society... recruiting members?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady, what's this about a society?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:57.03,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,My friends put it together to replace \Nthe theater club while it's on hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we'll be able \Nto do theater here at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you two want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll join!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.87,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, could you come to the \Ntheater club room later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:24.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a society now, \Nbut you'll still need to apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.64,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.01,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is great, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you friends with Chiaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking to her like you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What's going on between you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... ah... i-it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.89,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry, but who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I just introduced myself earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your classmate, Nakajima Yua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:52.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be an actress, and I enrolled in \Nthis school because of Chiaki-senpai's acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:01.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How can a little shrimp like you \Nbe friends with Chiaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.08,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! I might have gone too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.31,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's a nice person deep down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I still want to know what the deal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nakajima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:17.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan and I have \Nsomewhere we need to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.24,sign_9237_102_Theater_Club,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Theater Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're both here. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We ran into someone pretty powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see. There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.77,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are you really \Nplanning to join the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... um... Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never approve of you joining!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,A failure of a little shrimp like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, that's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:21.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A failshrimp like you isn't fit to be \Nin this theater club with Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.23,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you're not fit for Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have the guts \Nto stand on a stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.98,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are we interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:35.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um... well... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, um, are you \Nhoping to join the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.17,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Nakajima Yua.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.07,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan? That's a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I do something to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.64,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you saved Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You make such delicious coffee, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:28.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I heard you two \Njoined the theater club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.72,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a society now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.24,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the theater club \Nat its core, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All the club members are joining, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:45.87,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Hina-chan's goal of being \Nin theater at Fujimiya High has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:51.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... But we've only just \Nformed our theater troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Was it okay for us to join the theater club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.39,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just do both?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We can do both?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you'll be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:08.57,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There's another hurdle Hina-chan \Nneeds to get over first, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hurdle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I mean getting used to \Nbeing in front of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-In front of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:21.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about working part-time \Nin the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good. It's a \Nservice industry, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:29.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, try working here \Non your next day off from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Leave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:47.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I let Mayu-chan talk me \Ninto agreeing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:54.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Theater troupe, theater club, \Nserving customers part-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How am I gonna do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:05.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as I don't get nervous, \Nthings seem to work out okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all I can do is try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.89,sign_4149_24_Fujimiya__Girls_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimiya\N Girls'\N High
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:22.87,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,"I may be mistaken, \Nbut that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:28.78,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the bear's gall of \NNametoko Mountain is well-known."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.40,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the next passage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.73,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:43.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"I-It cures s-stomachaches \Nand m-makes wounds disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:47.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-At the N-N-Namari-no-Yu entrance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.41,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.35,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, go ahead, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.40,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san, you can sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,"It cures stomachaches and \Nmakes wounds disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,At the Namari-no-Yu entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:10.31,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a sign has long stood that \Nreads, 'Bear's gall here.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:10.31,Italics Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she... that scary girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.70,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.12,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.07,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me carry \Nthe handouts on the desk here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:28.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-U-U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.77,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:49.98,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.98,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Ye—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.10,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.23,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.44,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.37,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:08.74,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:09.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.15,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What should we eat on the way home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We're having dinner as soon as we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:27.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Eating books to hold myself over is kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.00,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The desserts there are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! I'd like one of these \Nand one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.78,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.39,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but which way is the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:51.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.18,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.29,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get to the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Just turn left at that traffic signal there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,then go straight, \Nand you'll see it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.51,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. \NYou've been such a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.35,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This'll show everyone that I can do \Nwhat that little failure can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:22.47,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How was that? Do you see \Nwhat a failshrimp you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:26.57,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The one fit for Chiaki-senpai \Nis me, Nakajima Yu—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.40,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Did I take that too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.08,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:38.58,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that way, Yua! \NYou must harden your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.30,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Look nowhere but forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.11,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.92,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She always covers for me when I fall short.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.19,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:05.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually putting on that uniform \Nmight be kind of embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You need guts, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Guts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Could I work at the used bookstore, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.68,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The bookstore is closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:20.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So that's why she's been \Nnodding off all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry parfait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:30.15,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll support you \Nall the way! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then... I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.08,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck. With everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.95,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you! It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This looks great, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:09.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayu-chan, is this really a uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It is, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Meow, meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Squee! You're too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.78,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, let's move \Nright on to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.78,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.07,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Changing outfits on a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.95,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I dozed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kuu-chan! You're awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm still dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.71,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess clean and pure really is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ready to get started now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:01.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done any work \Nother than being a scarecrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:05.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayu-chan, do you have any tips \Nfor serving customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.34,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's greeting them properly, \Nspeaking loudly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,and everything else \Ncan be solved with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.59,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We hardly get any customers, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:24.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I know Mayu-chan said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but what if we do get customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about serving customers \Nmakes me nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! I can't lose my confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:51.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Sorry I worried you. I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.81,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:04.07,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can that bird talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.66,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's got her hopes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there! I'm Toritarou, tweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here by yourself? \NAre you on a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:27.31,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No. I got lost and can't find my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:31.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's awful! Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know your home phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:37.82,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Then call your family with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll come for you, tweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.46,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little guilty somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:56.34,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello? Mommy? I'm at... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop Hitotose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.54,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a place called \N"Coffee Shop Hitotose."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:08.47,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh. I'm with a girl \Nin a really fancy costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welco—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:13.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, she seems to be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.11,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we've already called her mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's coming for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.41,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourself at home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.28,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.14,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to talk to her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.64,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all Toritarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:46.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Toritarou? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.89,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Toritarou and the lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.82,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.37,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Y...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're wellfrm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.86,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.04,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What a tiring day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:19.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to talk to a single \Ncustomer the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll completely fail both the theater troupe \Nand the theater club at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:29.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I really am a failshrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:38.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll try my hardest \Nto talk to that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move forward \Nif I keep talking about failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best at what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Time to take a step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.50,sign_4149_24_Fujimiya__Girls_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fujimiya \NGirls' \NHigh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:54.02,Main Dialogue,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:01.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nakajima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.39,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where'd you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So you're actually here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:20.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be bawling after learning \Nthat I'm the one fit for Chiaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.78,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe you wouldn't \Ncome to school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was wondering \Nwhat I'd do if you didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:36.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The landlady? Um, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.08,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What do I mean?! You realize \Nthat you're a failshrimp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,After all those times I covered for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me out so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:53.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's actually something \NI've been wanting to say to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:04.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,...f-f-f-friends with you, if you don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,F-Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.12,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure you're not mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:11.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to help you or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.08,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sakuragi-san, could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:20.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:27.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did not! That was a \Nconditioned reflex, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:29.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be really good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Let's just get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nakajima-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:48.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you Yua-chan from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:52.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.26,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:35.47,sign_33687_397_The_Scarecrow_He,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}The Scarecrow Heroine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:30.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad Hina-chan \Nseems to have made a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:33.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And the theater society's \Nactivities have begun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.64,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Hina-chan is practicing \Nlots of things every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "The Scarecrow Heroine."
